# Normalize all text to LF. This repo is built in WSL/Linux (SBF toolchain),
# so CRLF would break shell scripts (\r in shebang) and is undesirable for
# Rust sources. Binary artifacts are left untouched by `text=auto`.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.rs text eol=lf
*.toml text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
